ogram" target="_blank"> - 12 Month</a> CMU</p><p>(5) <a href="https://www.australia.cmu.edu/study/information-technology-management/msit-21-month-program" target="_blank">Master of Science in Information Technology (ITM) - 21 Month</a> CMU</p><p>(6) <a href="https://www.australia.cmu.edu/study/information-technology-management/msit-itm-information-security-specialisation" target="_blank">Master of Science in Information Technology - Information Technology Management (Information Security Specialisation)&nbsp;</a> CMU</p><p>(7) <a href="https://internationaleducation.gov.au/endeavour%20program/scholarships-and-fellowships/international-applicants/pages/international-applicants.aspx" target="_blank">International Applicants</a> CMU</p><p>(8) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/职业列表" target="_blank">Career</a> Outcomes and Data CMU</p><h3>商业智能与数据分析</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:17.9%">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/USNEWS排名" target="_blank">USNEWS排名</a></p>			</td>			<td style="width:8.32%">			<p>1</p>			</td>			<td style="width:13.3%">			<p>学费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:19.96%">			<p>$94,739</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.3%">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/申请截止日期" target="_blank">申请截止日期</a></p>			</td>			<td style="width:22.22%">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/滚动申请" target="_blank">滚动录取</a></p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:17.9%">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/TOEFL" target="_blank">TOEFL</a>要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:8.32%">			<p>88</p>			</td>			<td style="width:13.3%">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/GPA" target="_blank">GPA</a>要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:19.96%">			<p>无</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.3%">			<p>可申请学期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:22.22%">			<p>全年</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:17.9%">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/IELTS" target="_blank">IELTS</a>要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:8.32%">		