ess-intelligence-data-analytics/advanced-cert-in-bida-1" target="_blank">Advanced Certificate in Business Intelligence and Data Analytics​</a> CMU</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a href="https://www.australia.cmu.edu/study/business-intelligence-data-analytics/msit-bida-track" target="_blank">Master of Science in Information Technology (Business Intelligence &amp; Data Analytics)&nbsp;</a>CMU</p><p>(5)&nbsp;<a href="https://www.australia.cmu.edu/apply/international-students/entry-requirements-international-students" target="_blank">Entry Requirements</a>&nbsp;CMU</p><p>(6)&nbsp;<a href="https://www.australia.cmu.edu/apply/international-students/fees-and-scholarships-international-students" target="_blank">Fees and Scholarships</a>CMU</p><h3>公共政策与管理</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:97px">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/USNEWS排名" target="_blank">USNEWS排名</a></p>			</td>			<td style="width:46px">			<p>6</p>			</td>			<td style="width:71px">			<p>学费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:136px">			<p>AUD$78,960-$93,080</p>			</td>			<td style="width:98px">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/申请截止日期" target="_blank">申请截止日期</a></p>			</td>			<td style="width:119px">			<p>4月30日</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:97px">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/TOEFL" target="_blank">TOEFL</a>要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:46px">			<p>88</p>			</td>			<td style="width:71px">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/GPA" target="_blank">GPA</a>要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:136px">			<p>无</p>			</td>			<td style="width:98px">			<p>可申请学期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:119px">			<p>一学期</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:97px">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/IELTS" target="_blank">IELTS</a>要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:46px">			<p>6.5</p>			</td>			<td style="width:71px">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/GRE" target="_blank">GRE</a>要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:136px">			<p>Required</p>