-公私合作管理方向：</strong></p><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:316px">课程名称</td>			<td style="width:400px">课程英文名称</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td><strong>政府和社会资本合作课程</strong></td>			<td><strong>Public Private Partnerships (PPP) Curriculum</strong></td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td>PPP I ：理论与设计</td>			<td>PPP I : Theory and Design&nbsp;</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td>PPP II：发展国家实践</td>			<td>PPP II : Developing Countries Practice</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td>公共财政：理论与案例</td>			<td>Public Finance : Theories and Cases</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td>腐败，民主与发展</td>			<td>Corruption, Democracy and Development</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td>系统综合（应用PPP研究项目）</td>			<td>Systems Synthesis (Applied PPP Research Project)</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td><strong>与政府和社会资本合作相关的核心课程</strong></td>			<td><strong>Core Subjects : PPP related</strong></td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td>策略分析I</td>			<td>Policy Analysis I</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td>应用经济学分析I</td>			<td>Applied Economics Analysis I</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td>成本效益分析</td>			<td>Cost Benefit Analysis</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td>财务分析</td>			<td>Financial Analysis</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td><strong>其他核心课程</strong></td>			<td><strong>Other Core Subjects</strong></td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td>商业智能和分析</td>			<td>Business Intelligence and Analytics</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td>数据库管理概论</td>			<td>Introduction to Database Management</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td>决策</td>			<td>Decision Making Under Uncertainty</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td>战略演讲技巧</td>			<td>Strategic Presentation Skills&nbsp;</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td>专业写作（政策分析）</td>			<td>Professional Writing (Policy Analysis)</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td>组织设计与实施</td>			<td>Organization Design and Implementation</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td>战略规划</td>			<td>Strategic Planning</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td>应用经济学II</td>			<td>Applied Economics II</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td>统计方法</td>			<td>Statistical Methods</td>		</tr>	</tbody></table><p>*(7)</p><p><strong>奖学金项目</strong></p><p>卡耐基梅隆大学澳洲分校公共政策与管理项目（MSIT）向国际学生提供的<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/奖学金" target="_blank">奖学金<