target="_blank">计算金融</a>硕士（MS in Computational Finance）*(2)</li>	<li>产品服务创新硕士（Master of Integrated Innovation for Products &amp; Services (MIIPS)）：原名为产品开发硕士（Master of Product Development）：申请信息请见工程学院产品开发专业申请说明。*(3)</li>	<li>产品管理硕士（Master of Science in Product Management）：属于STEM项目，为期1年。*(4)</li>	<li>商业分析硕士（Online Master of Science in Business Analytics (MSBA)）：远程项目。*(5)</li>	<li>工商管理博士（PhD in Business Administration）*(6)</li>	<li>MBA双学位项目：	<ul>		<li>工商管理硕士/土木与环境工程（MBA Civil And Environmental Engineering）：与工程学院土木与环境工程系共同开设。</li>		<li>工商管理硕士/<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/软件工程" target="_blank">软件工程</a>（MBA/<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/软件工程" target="_blank">Software Engineering</a>）：与<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/计算机科学" target="_blank">计算机科学</a>学院和软件工程研究所共同开设。</li>		<li>工商管理硕士/医疗政策与管理（MBA/Health Care Policy And Management）：为期2.5年，与信息系统与公共政策学院共同开设。</li>		<li>工商管理硕士/<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/法学" target="_blank">法学</a>博士（MBA/Juris Doctorate (<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/法学" target="_blank">Law</a>)）：为期4年。</li>		<li>工商管理硕士/公共政策与管理（MBA/Public Policy and Management）：由商学院与公共政策与管理学院共同开设。</li>		<li>3+2工商管理硕士（3-2 MBA）：为期5年，面向卡耐基梅隆大学本科生招生。学生可在本科三年级申请，毕业之时，可获得学士和工商管理硕士两个学位。*(7)</li>	</ul>	</li>	<li>PhD双学位项目：	<ul>		<li>算法、组合与优化（Algorithms, Combinatorics, and Optimization）：与<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/数学" target="_blank">数学</a>和计算机系共同开设。</li>		<li>行为<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/经济学" target="_blank">经济学</a>（Behavioral Economics）：与人文与社会科学学院共同开设。</li>		<li>行为营销与决策研究（Behavioral Marketing And Decision Research）：与人文与社会科学学院共同开设。</li>		<li>经济与公共政策（Economics And Public Policy）：与公共政策与管理学院共同开设。*(8)</li>	</ul>	</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a href="https://www.cmu.edu/tepper/programs/mba/index.html" target="_blank">TEPPER SCHOOL MBA PROGRAM OPTIONS</a> Tepper School of Business, Carnegie Mellon University</p><p>(2) <a href="https://www.cmu.edu/mscf/" target="_blank">Master of Science in Computational Finance</a> Tepper School of Business, Carnegie Mellon University</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a href="https://www.cmu.edu/iii/degrees/miips/index.html" target="_blank">Master of Integrated Innovation for Products &amp; Services (MIIPS)</a>&nbsp;Tepper School of Business, Carnegie Mellon University</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a href="https://ms-product-management.cmu.edu/" target="_blank">Master of Science in Product Management</a>&nbsp;Tepper School of Business, Carnegie Mellon University</p><p>(5) <a href="https://analytics.tepper.cmu.edu/" target="_blank">Online Master of Science in Business Analytics (MSBA)</a>&nbsp;Tepper School of Business, Carnegie Mellon University</p><p>(6) <a href="https://www.cmu.edu/tepper/programs/phd/index.html" target="_blank">Ph.D. Program fields</a> Tepper School of Business, Carnegie Mellon University</p><p>(7) <a href="https://www.cmu.edu/tepper/programs/mba/curriculum/dual-and-joint-degrees/index.html" target="_blank">MBA Dual and Joint Degrees</a> Tepper School of Business, Carnegie Mellon University</p><p>(8) <a href="https://www.cmu.edu/tepper/programs/mba/curriculum/dual-and-joint-degrees/index.html" target="_blank">Joint Ph.D. Programs</a> Tepper School of Business, Carnegie Mellon University</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>MBA项目</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:16.0%">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/USNEWS排名" target="_blank">USNEWS排名</a></p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.0%">			<p>17</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.0%">			<p>学费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.0%">			<p>$68,000</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.0%">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/申请截止日期" target="_blank">申请截止日期</a></p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.0%">			<p>10月6日</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:16.0%">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/TOEFL" target="_blank">TOEFL</a>要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.0%">			<p>100</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.0%">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/GPA" target="_blank">GPA</a>要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.0%">			<p>平