chine Learning）：仅面向卡耐基梅隆大学的本科生*(8)</li>	<li>机器学习硕士（Secondary Masters in Machine Learning, SMML）：仅面向卡耐基梅隆大学在校博士生同时可以申请ML硕士*(9)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>机器学习系研究设置：Machine Learning Research</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=JrvWrUMHwSnOKhAi7ulkAQdvgETLTnUFeDykZ-Oc1hDVHzptg1lz9-MYknzfChgXk-WzlHhBA5Xl1dxMc0Y6fFeG-YZp" target="_blank">Masters Admissions</a>&nbsp;Carnegie Mellon</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Gr-dDkOkwhmWQRZyJJJJJsQVZWuwBGQgqIAIA3f2B3f2vd8P_9ueqxeEBIu4BzYS2lkq2iK41ikOc75N878DdHkDcHodwxkj1iXDpxKjNsK4tikOc7L" target="_blank">Masters Admissions - Frequently Asked Questions</a>&nbsp;Carnegie Mellon</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a href="https://www.cmu.edu/sfs/tuition/graduate/index.html" target="_blank">2019-2020&nbsp;Graduate Tuition &amp; Fees Information</a>&nbsp;Carnegie Mellon</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a href="https://www.ml.cmu.edu/academics/machine-learning-phd.html" target="_blank">PhD Program in Machine Learning</a>&nbsp;Carnegie Mellon</p><p>(5)&nbsp;<a href="https://applygrad.cs.cmu.edu/apply/index.php?domain=1" target="_blank">PhD Program in ML</a>&nbsp;Carnegie Mellon</p><p>(6)&nbsp;<a href="https://www.ml.cmu.edu/academics/primary-ms-machine-learning-masters.html" target="_blank">Master of Science in Machine Learning</a>&nbsp;Carnegie Mellon</p><p>(7)&nbsp;FAQ&#39;s for ML Masters Program&nbsp;Carnegie Mellon</p><p>(8)&nbsp;<a href="https://www.ml.cmu.edu/academics/5th-year-ms.html" target="_blank">5th Yr. Masters in Machine Learning</a>&nbsp;Carnegie Mellon</p><p>(9)&nbsp;<a href="https://www.ml.cmu.edu/academics/secondary-ms.html" target="_blank">Secondary Masters in Machine Learning, SMML</a>&nbsp;Carnegie Mellon</p><h3>机器人研究</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:80px">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/USNEWS排名" target="_blank">USNEWS排名</a></p>			</td>			<td style="width:66px">			<p>1</p>			</td>			<td style="