nk">WES</a>公证递交</p><p>（3）申请费：$100</p><p>（4）TOELF/IELTS成绩</p><p>（5）个人作品</p><p>除个人作品要求外，其<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/申请材料" target="_blank">申请材料</a>及方式均与一般专业的申请无异。*(3)</p><p><strong>专业设置</strong></p><ul>	<li>器乐（Instrumental Performance）</li>	<li>电子琴（Keyboard Performance）</li>	<li>声乐（Vocal Performance）</li>	<li>作曲（Composition）</li>	<li>音乐与技术（Music &amp; Technology）*(4)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a href="https://www.cmu.edu/cfa/music/apply/international-students.html" target="_blank">International Graduate Admission-School of Music</a> Carnegie Mellon</p><p>(2) <a href="https://www.cmu.edu/cfa/music/programs/graduate-programs/index.html" target="_blank">Graduate Programs-School of Music</a> Carnegie Mellon</p><p>(3) <a href="https://www.cmu.edu/cfa/music/apply/graduate_admission/graduate_application_requirements.html" target="_blank">Application Requirements-School of Music</a> Carnegie Mellon</p><p>(4) AREAS OF STUDY-School of Music Carnegie Mellon</p><p>(5) <a href="https://www.cmu.edu/sfs/tuition/graduate/cfa.html" target="_blank">Tuition</a>&nbsp;Carnegie Mellon</p><h2>人文学院</h2><p><strong>机构设置</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:115px">			<p><strong>院系名称</strong></p>			</td>			<td style="width:147px">			<p><strong>院系英文名</strong></p>			</td>			<td style="width:109px">			<p><strong>联系方式</strong></p>			</td>			<td style="width:197px">			<p><strong>邮件或网站地址</strong></p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:115px">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/英语" target="_blank">英语</a>系</p>			</td>			<td style="width:147px">			<p>English</p>			</td>			<td style="width:109px">			<p>(412) 268-2850</p>			</td>			<td style="width:197px">			<p>kpawlik@andrew.cmu.edu</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:115px">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/历史" target="_blank">历史</a>系</p>			</td>			<td style="width:147px">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/历史" target="_blank">History</a></p>			</td>			<td style="width:109p